# Operational distributed loads, long format (time x station)
# Source     : demo amplitudes scaled in time. Spatial grid aligned with
#              blade_spanwise_distribution.dat (spanwise_pos, radial_pos).
# Convention : SI units (s, m, N, N*m). Per-unit-span quantities use "/m".
# Datum      : section frame; q_y is flapwise, q_z is edgewise, m_x is twist per unit span.
# Layout     : long format. Each row is one (t, z) sample; t advances slowest.
#
# Schema (in column order):
#   t_s            [s]       time
#   spanwise_pos   [m]       spanwise position z
#   radial_pos     [m]       radial position r from rotor centre
#   q_y_Npm        [N/m]     distributed flapwise force per unit span
#   q_z_Npm        [N/m]     distributed edgewise force per unit span
#   m_x_Nmpm       [N*m/m]   distributed twisting moment per unit span
#
# units: s, m, m, N/m, N/m, N*m/m
